## Typography

### Font Family

- **Sans:** Outfit (matches logo wordmark - geometric, rounded 'O')
- **Mono:** JetBrains Mono (for code, legal citations)

### Type Scale

| Element | Classes | Usage |
|---------|---------|-------|
| Display | `text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight` | Hero headlines |
| H1 | `text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight` | Page titles |
| H2 | `text-2xl font-semibold` | Section headers |
| H3 | `text-xl font-medium` | Card titles |
| Body Large | `text-lg leading-relaxed` | Intro paragraphs |
| Body | `text-base leading-relaxed` | Default text |
| Small | `text-sm` | Secondary text |
| Caption | `text-xs font-medium tracking-wide` | Labels, badges |

### Legal Document Text

For legal content, use extra line height for readability:

```tsx
<p className="text-base leading-7">
  // Legal document text with generous line height
</p>
```

