## Components

### Buttons

```tsx
// Primary CTA - use gradient variant
<Button variant="gradient" size="lg">
  Start Free Trial
</Button>

// Standard actions
<Button variant="default">Submit</Button>

// Secondary actions
<Button variant="secondary">Cancel</Button>

// Outline for emphasis without filling
<Button variant="outline">Learn More</Button>

// Ghost for toolbar/nav actions
<Button variant="ghost" size="icon">
  <Icon />
</Button>
```

### Cards

```tsx
// Default card
<Card>
  <CardHeader>
    <CardTitle>Title</CardTitle>
    <CardDescription>Description</CardDescription>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>Content</CardContent>
</Card>

// Featured card - with glow (for pricing, features)
<Card variant="featured">

// Glass card - on gradient backgrounds
<Card variant="glass">

// Elevated - for floating elements
<Card variant="elevated">
```

### Spacing

Use Tailwind spacing scale consistently:

- **Component padding:** `p-6` (default), `p-8` (featured)
- **Section spacing:** `py-16 lg:py-24`
- **Gap between items:** `gap-4` (tight), `gap-6` (default), `gap-8` (loose)
- **Max content width:** `max-w-7xl` (marketing), `max-w-4xl` (reading)

