## What NOT to Do (Avoid Generic AI Look)

### ❌ DON'T

- Use chat bubbles for AI responses
- Add floating orbs/blobs backgrounds
- Use robot avatars or AI assistant faces
- Add "typing..." indicators like chatbots
- Use generic "tech blue" (#0066FF)
- Copy ChatGPT's interface patterns

### ✅ DO

- Use document-style interfaces (like Notion, Linear)
- Show structured, formatted responses
- Use the Orderly brand blue (#3B5EEB)
- Design like a legal tool that happens to use AI
- Prioritise clarity and scanability
- Use professional, subtle animations

