## Australian Localisation

### Date/Time Formats

```tsx
// ✅ Australian format
const date = new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-AU'); // DD/MM/YYYY

// Time format
const time = new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-AU', { 
  hour: '2-digit', 
  minute: '2-digit' 
}); // 14:30
```

### Spelling

Use Australian English:
- colour (not color)
- organisation (not organization)
- analyse (not analyze)
- licence (noun) / license (verb)

